{"tid":1307733,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[請廣傳]下次比藍絲廢中廢老打，一定要還手","createTime":"2019-07-11T16:34:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-12T01:46:27.000Z","uid":64948,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"12606308fb40a6ccb299fc8d16a43c3efb5f3492","tid":1307733,"uid":64948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T16:34:02.000Z","msg":"大埔有同路人比人打到骨裂之後<br />\n唔好再同我講面對班藍絲要打不還手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你地成日講以武制暴，又驚打完人比班狗告<br />\n而家就教精你，打完人都唔會有事<br />\n有無聽過<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">101拘捕令A條呀</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">下次比班藍絲打個陣，做足以下步驟:<br />\n1.對方郁手，請即還拖<br />\n2.叫身邊人開始拍片（呢樣唔難呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你地咁撚鐘意見到有人比人打就影人），拍低以下你要講既野<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">你剛剛干犯左傷人罪行，我而家(?)點(?)分報警求助，係警察來到前，你唔可以逃跑，反抗，否則我會用「101拘捕令A條」賦予既市民拘捕權，用合理適當既武力將你制服直至到你唔再反抗，逃跑，或警察到達現場</span></span><br />\n<br />\n唔好再同我講比人打要和理非<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">仁者無勇 便成犬儒</span></span>"},{"pid":"b8a11cdf5d321efe01651a064843717debb6ee81","tid":1307733,"uid":64948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T16:34:13.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"a93a14195f8560f28d3d4769f0186185a990b210","tid":1307733,"uid":64948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T16:34:26.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"6226c35fb2e6c67837604407f2de6b0832c764c3","tid":1307733,"uid":64948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T16:34:37.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"ab61da8af6b2769207baf6e16f22f9290d4a45a0","tid":1307733,"uid":64948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T16:34:50.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"cf21991e1a8d22dfae35ebd49f33b88f4b42c72f","tid":1307733,"uid":62011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T16:36:55.000Z","msg":"用索帶啦。<br />\n打死廢老無著數。"},{"pid":"164e6c386b